data.current_description: Starts asynchronous cancellation on a long-running operation. The server makes a best effort to cancel the operation, but success is not guaranteed. On successful cancellation, the operation remains in the system with a CANCELLED error status (code 1) rather than being deleted. Use GetOperation to verify cancellation status.
